{"id": 2315, "genre": 1001, "title": "在亲密关系 or 友情中，你发现过哪些“对方在疏远你”的征兆？", "description": "不需要明说，我已经看出来了。（题图来自：iStock©dane_mark）", "record_count": 3223, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180502173605iTSKb9AypIzdwO2x.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-11T05:42:03Z", "options": [{"id": 286721, "content": "害怕游戏里遇到尴尬，便放弃了这款游戏…………", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366686}, {"id": 287233, "content": "和别人在一起比和我在一起更开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1049087}, {"id": 287745, "content": "我发十条，他回一天，或者不回", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377140}, {"id": 295426, "content": "打电话打了比较久，或者是你听出来他语气有点激动。\n电话挂了之后——\n“谁的电话？”\n“一个朋友。”\n“哦，怎么了呢？”\n“没怎么。”\n……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417486}, {"id": 287747, "content": "在我话痨开心找他聊天时突然不耐烦π_π", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335272}, {"id": 286987, "content": "分享事情 他们只是再嗯啊哦的敷衍我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372204}, {"id": 286733, "content": "有这么一种朋友，就是不太主动联系人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338463}, {"id": 286989, "content": "开始很忙了，忙到没时间联系，不再把她的事情分享给你，她的一些东西是从别人的口中知道的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373063}, {"id": 288270, "content": "恍然間发现，好久没见面了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378608}, {"id": 287759, "content": "从最开始的秒回到后来半天后一句到最后只发空格和表情包", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377272}, {"id": 286481, "content": "不再主动聊天了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 383, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367681}, {"id": 286482, "content": "恢复消息时间很长而且语气很官方", "image": null, "praise_count": 501, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368608}, {"id": 286483, "content": "她/他谈了男/女朋友我竟然是通过朋友圈才知道的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 154, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572462}, {"id": 286484, "content": "发消息会特意躲开我的视线范围", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572462}, {"id": 286485, "content": "不会主动联系你", "image": null, "praise_count": 284, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237927}, {"id": 286486, "content": "抢话", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226893}, {"id": 286487, "content": "第六感", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371180}, {"id": 287255, "content": "在一起的时候渐渐没了话语", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374465}, {"id": 286488, "content": "经常隔天才回复微信消息（很明显了", "image": null, "praise_count": 117, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5538}, {"id": 286489, "content": "热情地发消息过去得到的都是哦 好 嗯 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687231}, {"id": 286490, "content": "大家是谈性色变么 评论好少?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966594}, {"id": 296218, "content": "眼神与说辞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332009}, {"id": 286491, "content": "找她出去都会用各种理由推辞掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291755}, {"id": 286492, "content": "约出去一直说没空", "image": null, "praise_count": 102, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350439}, {"id": 286494, "content": "不想理她，她说的都不感兴趣，因为她带来的都是不开心，还不如我刷个视频，玩个游戏开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371209}, {"id": 286750, "content": "嗯嗯。哦。呵呵。……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372072}, {"id": 289822, "content": " 时间是流动的水，而我们不过是水下的沙子，分开是自然定律，分不开是人为因素。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386327}, {"id": 286495, "content": "不再第一时间评论/点赞你的朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 286497, "content": "不愿意再跟你说她的私事", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370821}, {"id": 286498, "content": "不对我发脾气了\n不再因为“今天天气这么好你居然不和我出来玩”而生气了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357035}, {"id": 287778, "content": "对我越来越冷淡了，越来越不在乎了，和最初的样子完全不一样，最初的样子和现在的样子，我始终记得", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377496}, {"id": 286499, "content": "不会主动联系你，你每次主动联系的时候，得到的回答都是嗯，噢……", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371240}, {"id": 286500, "content": "看见他的朋友圈都不想点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367155}, {"id": 286501, "content": "不回我微信，但是我却知道她看了。\n不在一个生活圈，很难聊到一块儿了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355663}, {"id": 290853, "content": "朋友圈屏蔽了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391330}, {"id": 286502, "content": "相互约过多次聚会，均未成行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371241}, {"id": 286759, "content": "更多的想知道为什么\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371676}, {"id": 286504, "content": "在一起时不知道聊什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369290}, {"id": 286505, "content": "评论里的都是我自己的症状肿么办。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013245}, {"id": 286508, "content": "朋友圈分组显示", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340338}, {"id": 287533, "content": "她回来我居然是从她的朋友圈里得知的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375607}, {"id": 286510, "content": "其实字里行间可以感受得到", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366230}, {"id": 286511, "content": "说过了晚安却在出生岛相遇。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 45325}, {"id": 287791, "content": "当我发现很多同感的时候，我就输了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377645}, {"id": 286512, "content": "很遗憾 没亲密的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084725}, {"id": 286513, "content": "不再给你点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252093}, {"id": 287282, "content": "嗯，哦，好，行，我睡觉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374284}, {"id": 286517, "content": "表情不再丰富", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371308}, {"id": 286519, "content": "嘲笑我不会吹口哨", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914579}, {"id": 287031, "content": "现在的婚姻状态，以上都是", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373193}]}